In Task 1, I created a digital literacy awareness infographic using Canva. The infographic was designed to explain the concept of digital literacy and its importance for students. It covered key topics such as safe internet practices, useful digital tools, and maintaining a professional online presence.

The design included visual elements like icons, headings, and short descriptions to make the information easy to understand. Canva provided a user-friendly interface with various templates and design options, which made the creation process smooth and efficient.

One challenge I faced was selecting the right content and organizing it in a visually appealing way within a single page. However, it was also interesting to learn how design and content can be combined to effectively communicate information.

Overall, this task helped me improve my creativity and understand how to present information clearly.
